sourceMeaningMnemonic: Your <radical>clan</radical> is breaking <radical>ground</radical> and <radical>building</radical> your new <kanji>residence</kanji>. You're all working together to make you a new home!
meaningInfo: Picture your clan, working together, to build a new residence for you on their land.
readingMnemonic: Your new <kanji>residence</kanji> is complete! You step closer and the smell of <reading>ta</reading>ter (<ja>てい</ja>) tots hits your nose. Someone is making you tater tots in your new residence. Wait, no they aren't. Your residence is MADE of tater tots! Thank you, clan!
readingInfo: Imagine living in a tater tot residence. Whenever you're hungry, you just lean over to the wall and munch.
